thread.title: L. Erickson
thread.title_full: Transport Luxury Auto reviewed by L. Erickson

author: L. Erickson
title: L. Erickson
text:
I moved from California to the East Coast, I had my car sent inside the large carrier, not only are the rates competitive but my car arrived on time and the drivers were all very professional.
I would definitely recommend Transport Luxury and if you speak with Shane you will be sure to get terrific service.
L. Erickson
